{"word":"προσκολλάω","slug":"προσκολλάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προσϰολλάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κολλάω\">κολλάω</a></el> ‘to glue, join’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el>ϰόλλα</el> ‘glue’] in imagery of adherence; only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> and in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>cling to, stick to, remain joined,</b> of marital commitment <b><a href='B:470 19:5'>Mt 19:5</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:480 10:7'>Mk 10:7</a>; <a href='B:560 5:31'>Eph 5:31</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πρόσκλισις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πρόσκομμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}